/* Hand-authored fixture: a two-part assembly with AP214 product structure
   (PRODUCT / PRODUCT_DEFINITION / NEXT_ASSEMBLY_USAGE_OCCURRENCE).  Horizon's
   importer does not map assembly structure yet (documented limitation) —
   the expected behavior is that both parts import as independent solids and
   the product structure is ignored.  Parts: two tetrahedra with legs 10,
   the second translated +20 in X.  Volume of each = 1000/6. */
